text: Dumki () is an upazila of Patuakhali District in the Division of Barisal, Bangladesh. == Administration == Dumki Upazila is divided into five union parishads: Angaria, Labukhali, Muradia, Pangasia, and Sreerampur. The union parishads are subdivided into 21 mauzas and 24 villages. ==Educational institutions== * Patuakhali Science and Technology University == Related pages == *Upazilas of Bangladesh *Districts of Bangladesh *Divisions of Bangladesh == References == Category:Upazilas of Patuakhali District
